&lt;p&gt;With COVID-19 continuing to play a major part in all our everyday lives, we are expanding our capacity over the winter period and need your support to help continuing deliver excellent care to our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Group of Bank highly skilled, Band 6 Bank Dietitians with a passion for community services and HPC registration to join our temporary workers, in the heart of London!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a flexible Bank worker, you are employed on an ‘as and when required’ basis or a long-term assignment, whichever suits you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skills required:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing own caseload of domiciliary and care home clients requiring oral nutrition support with a small number of enteral feeding cases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong clinical background and be able to demonstrate knowledge, skills and previous experience in the area of nutrition support and enteral feeding.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Although not essential, previous experience of working in the community setting would be an advantage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return for your skills and experience we can offer you:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive hourly rates (based on experience)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to the NHS Pension Scheme (subject to status)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid annual leave &lt;br /&gt;Access to Statutory &amp; Mandatory training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to sample different areas of work across or work within different groups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you are excited by the above then we would love to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our temporary staffing shifts are calculated hourly and paid weekly. You are paid only for the hours you actually work during any Assignment. Bank workers are paid on fixed third point based on the Agenda for Change (AFC) pay bands.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Weekly pay will include: Basic pay + HCAS + 12.07% Holiday pay + Unsocial hours (If applicable)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check out the CLCH trust Facebook, twitter &amp; LinkedIn webpages for more information about us.&lt;/p&gt;
